org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabCommit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabCommit

  • public final class GitlabCommit
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Commit. This doesn't support create, update, and delete operations. This supports query for commits within GitlabProject. See GitlabCommit.ProjectQuery. Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/commits.html

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  GitlabCommit.ProjectQuery
      This extends GitlabQuery and supports query for GitlabCommits within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range.
